      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MCGEE (3) form has been hard to fault. Finished second at his latest appearance over 2503m at this track, beaten 2 metres, on the back of a couple of wins, the most recent at Pinjarra. No excuses from this advantageous draw and has the class to return to the winners' list. MAJESTIC GA GA (5) resumes from a spell of three-and-a-half months after closing off last campaign in good form, scoring at her last appearance over 2130m here. Sure to be right there at the finish. MYSTERY FRED (4) is one of the main contenders after winning his past three starts, the latest at Pinjarra eight days ago. Difficult to ignore that sort of form. MRIYA DREAM (2) was out of the money two runs ago then broke and finished sixth last start over 2185m at Pinjarra, coming home 30 metres from the winner. Has the benefit of a good draw and rates a live chance in a similar assignment.",
